          <title>Supplementary Figure S3</title>
          <p><bold>Two representative genes showing clear spatial APA usage patterns but no gene expression pattern</bold> The “Gene” row is the average gene expression level of the respective gene in all spots which represented by the sum of expression levels of poly(A) sites in the gene. The “RUD” row is the average RUD score of the gene in all spots.</p>
        </caption>
        <media xlink:href="mmc3.pptx"/>
      </supplementary-material>
    </p>
